Create an ultra-detailed, professional multi-column strategic roadmap diagram in infographic style.
The visual structure must follow a vertical timeline with horizontal branching, similar to enterprise project roadmaps and product development pipelines.
Use clean rectangular color blocks, consistent spacing, connector lines, and timeline markers.
The roadmap must cover Years 2025–2030, each represented as a separate vertical section containing sub-blocks for quarters and activities.
Style should match corporate roadmap layouts:
– neatly aligned columns
– color-coded task categories
– arrows showing progression
– grouped clusters with titles
– readable typography
– organized hierarchical flow like a product lifecycle chart.

